OL,3,CPensioner jailed for sexual assault of
OL,4,Cteenager in leisure centre sauna
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for sexually
OL,7,Fassaulting a young man with severe
OL,8,Flearning difficulties at a leisure
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FThe assault happened in the sauna at
OL,12,FHyndburn Leisure Centre in Accrington
OL,13,Fon 16 January 2022.
OL,15,FStephen Tate, 69, approached his
OL,16,Fvictim, a then 19-year-old with severe
OL,17,Flearning difficulties, and without
OL,18,Fwarning performed a sexual act on him.
