OL,3,CPensioner jailed for sexual assault of
OL,4,Cteenager in leisure centre sauna
OL,6,FThe victim told his father and pointed
OL,7,Fout Tate to him, who then got into his
OL,8,Fblack BMW and drove off.
OL,10,FThe victim's dad took note of the
OL,11,Fvehicle registration number and
OL,12,Freported the matter to the police.
OL,14,FTate, from Church in Lancashire, was
OL,15,Farrested and later charged with
OL,16,Fengaging in sexual activity with a
OL,17,Fperson with a mental disorder impeding
OL,18,Fchoice.
