OL,3,CPensioner jailed for sexual assault of
OL,4,Cteenager in leisure centre sauna
OL,6,FHe was found guilty following a trial
OL,7,Fat Preston Crown Court in December
OL,8,F2024. At his sentencing on 29 April he
OL,9,Fwas jailed for six years.
OL,11,FHe was also ordered to sign the Sex
OL,12,FOffenders Register for life and was
OL,13,Fbarred from working with children and
OL,14,Fvulnerable people.
OL,16,FTate was also made subject of a 10-
OL,17,Fyear sexual harm prevention order,
OL,18,Fwhich bans him from entering any
OL,19,Fpublic sauna, steam room or solarium.
