OL,6,FIn an impact statement to the court,
OL,7,Fthe victim's dad said: "Our son's
OL,8,Fdisability has delayed and severely
OL,9,Fsuffered his recovery from this
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,F"We do not know how long this will
OL,13,Ftake but the mental scars will stay
OL,14,Fwith him for life. We cannot explain
OL,15,Fhow this has truly impacted his mental
OL,16,Fwellbeing, confidence and self-esteem
OL,17,Fbut this incident has certainly taken
OL,18,Faway his limited enjoyment in his life.
